<h1 class="doc-page-title">DDT Standards Management</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Create, manage, and publish DDT (Digital, Data and Technology) standards with approval workflow and version control.</p>

<p>Documentation for DDT standards management is being developed. This will cover:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Creating and editing DDT standards</li>
    <li>Standards workflow (Draft, Under Review, Approved, Published, Rejected, Archived)</li>
    <li>Categories and sub-categories</li>
    <li>Approval workflow</li>
    <li>Version control</li>
    <li>Publishing standards</li>
</ul>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <p class="mb-0">For user stories and detailed feature information, see <a href="@Url.Action("UserStories", "Documentation")">User stories</a>.</p>
